definition.en: A citation or reference to another creative work, such as another publication, web page, scholarly article, etc.
definition.de: Verweis von einem Dokument auf ein anderes. Z. B. eine andere Publikation, Webseite, wissenschaftliche Referenz, etc.
definition.fr: Citation d'un document dans un autre document. A citation or reference to another creative work, such as another publication, web page, scholarly article, etc.
definition.es: Cita de una obra creativa en otro documento. A citation or reference to another creative work, such as another publication, web page, scholarly article, etc.
